import React from 'react'
import Input from './Input'
const Login = () => {
  return (
    <from>
    <Input
    type="text"
    placeholder="Username"
    />
    <Input
    type="password"
    placeholder="Password"
    />
    <button> Enter</button>
    </from>
    
  )
}

export default Login
